body:
After 2 yeras.... ch. 9. I thought Izayoi for get about this story. There will be one more chapter. I wonder how will it end. And yeah she is already pregnant, and because of the number of different partners she gave her body, there is no way to know who is the father. Marriage is only for "show" and to avoid another scandal.

I hope some day Izayoi Seishin works will be less censorship....
